<div class='talk-speaker__details media__message'>
<div class='talk-speaker__name h10'>
<a class="l3 talk-speaker__link" href="/speakers/mary_robinson">Mary Robinson</a>
</div>
<div class='talk-speaker__description'>
Global leader
</div>
<div class='talk-speaker__bio'>
Mary Robinson served as president of Ireland from 1990 to 1997, and as UN High Commissioner for Human Rights from 1997 to 2002. She now leads a foundation devoted to climate justice.
<a class="l3 talk-speaker__link" href="/speakers/mary_robinson">Full bio</a>
</div>
